edu.cnm.deepdive.ak.budgetingapp

Class ItemDetailActivity

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.cnm.deepdive.ak.budgetingapp.ItemDetailActivity

  • public class ItemDetailActivity
extends java.lang.Object
    An activity representing a single Item detail screen. This activity is only used narrow width devices. On tablet-size devices, item details are presented side-by-side with a list of items in a CategoryListActivity.
